title: The Rise And Fall Of Leon House- Chapter 1 - By J.T. Manis
description:
When a series of murders is committed that leaves police forces baffled, high school detective Leon House takes on the case to see if it takes the place of his boredom. Instead, what he finds is much deeper and darker than anyone should ever have to face.

This is only chapter one of the finished draft. The final product will be released in early 2009 as a major publication.
